productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
I tried to pinch it but got peanut all over it.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
